{"tid":159990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陸4男女躲後車箱　偷渡遭美警犬抓包","createTime":"2017-03-17T11:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T11:38:52.000Z","uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"578f48f95d3506e62e452aff8e002734ec38f953","tid":159990,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"2017年03月17日17:26<br />\n<br />\n中國環球往今天援引美國媒體指出，一名美國男子在當地時間周二（14日），從墨西哥駕車進入美國被捕，海關官員在其後車廂，發現了4名中國非法移民。<br />\n據美國海關和邊境保護局發佈的新聞稿，當天下午5時45分，該名美籍男子（24歲）駕駛一輛2014款克萊斯勒轎車，從美墨邊境小鎮聖伊西德羅穿越邊境，但過境時被一隊警犬小組發現車尾箱有異常，負責邊檢的警察打開後車廂後，見有3名女子及1名男子緊緊蜷縮在裡面。報導稱他們都是中國公民。<br />\n美國海關官員稱，這4人沒有合法進入美國的證件，已扣留他們，等司法訴訟結束後，將驅逐他們離境。<br />\n該名司機將面臨聯邦移民偷渡的罪名，其汽車已被扣押。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170317/640_d601489c2b622a4d7efcce447d4ca365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170317%2F640_d601489c2b622a4d7efcce447d4ca365.jpg&h=99d74818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170317/1078651/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170317%2F1078651%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=493b5a94\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170317/1078651/</a>"},{"pid":"76cd1918f24685fbb74d45cbb1fb23a06ce2e5d6","tid":159990,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"不愛國了嗎"},{"pid":"091815bcfd3e30c4dd0ecd9e766f0034dd12c72f","tid":159990,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"你們是不是中國人"},{"pid":"8cebd1d160b7bfa56c50371bcfde88d6500ce52c","tid":159990,"uid":37011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"Build the wall!!!"}]}